This is supposed to be an ingredient checklist made for the cooking TEAM BUTTER.

There's a bug with Compass and Mountain Lion and Ruby 1.8 (don't forget to use compass watch --poll to work around this [mostly a note for myself])

Goal: (MVP)
Have a list of ingredients and generate a shopping list using Javascript

Long Term Goals Include: 
Being able to scrape recipe sites for ingredients
Storing ingredients 
Using Cookies to save place
etc... 